<synopsis><code mime="text/x-python">
@accepts(gint)
@returns(none)
def set_repeat_count(count)
</code></synopsis>
<p>Sets the number of times the @timeline should repeat.</p><p>If @count is 0, the timeline never repeats.</p><p>If @count is -1, the timeline will always repeat until
it's stopped.</p>

